OK

sample.data<-sample.data |> 
  mutate(item2_r=6-item2,
         item3_r=6-item3,
         total=item1+item2+item3,
         total_centered=total-mean(total),
         total_zscore=(total-mean(total))/sd(total))

sample.data<-sample.data |> 
  mutate(item2_c = item2-mean(item2),
         item3_c = item3-mean(item3),
         interaction_2_3=item2_c*item3_c)

sample.data$ABC<-sample(c("A","B","C"),100,T)

sample.data<-sample.data |> 
    mutate(ABC2num=as.numeric(as.factor(ABC)))

sample.data<-sample.data |> 
    mutate(
      ABC2num2ABC=recode(
        as.factor(ABC2num), 
        '1' = 'A', 
        '2' = 'B',
        '3' = 'C'))

sample.data<-sample.data |> 
  mutate(ABC2num2ABC=factor(ABC2num, 
                    levels=c("1", "2","3"), 
                labels=LETTERS[1:3])
  )
